item.title: CVE-2023-4150|2024-08-02T07:17:12.196Z -- unknown -- user%20activity%20tracking%20and%20log
item.description: The User Activity Tracking and Log WordPress plugin before 4.0.9 does not have proper CSRF checks when managing its license, which could allow attackers to make logged in admins update and deactivate the plugin's license via CSRF attacks
